<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type'/>
</head>
<body>
<h1>Confirmation email not sent</h1>
<p>The following dataset has been successfully deposited in the Illinois Data Bank, but the confirmation email was not sent:</p>
<blockquote>
    <%= @dataset.plain_text_citation %>
</blockquote>
<p>Here is some information about the deposited dataset:</p>
<blockquote>
    <p>DataCite DOI: <%= @dataset.identifier %></p>

    <p>Release date: <%= @dataset.release_date %></p>

    <p>Depositor: <%= @dataset.depositor_name %></p>

    <p>Contact person: <%= @dataset.corresponding_creator_name %></p>

    <p>Deposit agreement link:
        <a href="<%= IDB_CONFIG[:root_url_text] %>/datasets/<%= @dataset.key %>/review_deposit_agreement"><%= IDB_CONFIG[:root_url_text] %>
            /datasets/<%= @dataset.key %>/review_deposit_agreement</a></p>
</blockquote>

<p>
    Error:
    <%= @err.to_yml %>
</p>

<%= render partial: "sigblock_html" %>

</body>
</html>